<td></td>
<td valign="top">Keeping up with developments is fuelling my work in research. The impact of technology on our work and learning, as well as empowering people to take their lives into their own hands are my focal points.</td>
<td></td>
<td valign="top">Technology, work forms and organizational structures are all tools. Tools need to support people in their work, not the other way around. Social media are in sync with how we know people work, not how we wish them to work.</td>
